component.documentation:
@author Antoine Taillefer(ataillefer@nuxeo.com)
This service provides an API for synchronizing documents with a file system. It allows the following actions: - get a document - get a folder's children - create a folder - create a file - update a file - delete a document - rename a document - move a document - copy a document
It is used by Nuxeo Drive to synchronize the server with a client device.
